TopicTitle: SpaceY Heavy Lifters Mod Part Shine

Articles.Content: Hello! I have a relatively lightly-modded version of KSP, and I wanted to install the SpaceY Heavy Lifters Part pack. Issue is...a lot of the fuel tanks and boosters have a really annoying texture shine, like they're clipped with other parts. I'm not sure if this is happening with anyone else, or perhaps I'm just using the incorrect install?
Look at the troubleshooting section at the bottom of the first post.
